"Wow, who would have thought? Just a boy from Santurce, Puerto Rico, and now an Emmy nominated makeup artist! I'm absolutely ecstatic and feel like a winner already. This nomination is dedicated to all the kids from Llorens Torres, my hood. It's a testament to how dreams can become a reality no matter the circumstances you're given in life. Never give up, because anything is possible!" I also want to congratulate the Glam Team on the 
@tamronhallshow for always being such an amazing group of people to work with. I am truly honored to be a part of such a special team! #NeverGiveUp #DreamBig #AnythingIsPossible #daytimeemmynominee #daytimeemmys

🎵🎨 Unleashing creativity without limits! 🎨🎵

Hey everyone! 👋 As a DJ, music producer, and makeup artist, I refuse to be confined by boundaries. My passion for blending beats and creating captivating sounds is just as strong as my love for transforming faces with makeup artistry. Why choose one path when I can excel in both?

I thrive on pushing the boundaries of creativity, breaking the mold, and defying expectations. Whether I’m crafting a killer remix or painting a stunning masterpiece on someone’s canvas, my art knows no limits. I’m all about embracing the unexpected, fusing different worlds, and letting my imagination run wild.

So here’s to the rule-breakers, the genre-blenders, and the creative chameleons. Let’s keep pushing the envelope, celebrating diversity, and proving that creativity knows no bounds. Stay tuned for more musical and visual adventures, because with me, there’s always something new around the corner. 🎶💄✨ #UnleashCreativity #NoBoundaries

🌅🚀 Thank you for an unforgettable night! 🚀🌅

To everyone who joined us at Forever Sunsets and Forever Space, your energy made the night truly special. It was an honor to see each of you dancing and partying with pure joy. Your enthusiasm and love for music created an incredible atmosphere, and I’m grateful for every moment we shared. Let’s keep the party vibes alive and the memories burning bright. Your presence made it all worthwhile, and I can’t wait for the next adventure together. Thank you for rocking the dance floor and making the night one for the books! 🎉🎶 

🌅🚀 ¡Gracias por una noche inolvidable! 🚀🌅

Para todos los que nos acompañaron en Forever Sunsets y Forever Space, su energía hizo que la noche fuera realmente especial. Fue un honor verlos a cada uno de ustedes bailando y festejando con pura alegría. Tu entusiasmo y amor por la música crearon una atmósfera increíble y estoy agradecido por cada momento que compartimos. Mantengamos viva la vibra de fiesta y los recuerdos brillantes. Tu presencia hizo que todo valiera la pena y no puedo esperar a vivir la próxima aventura juntos. ¡Gracias por hacer vibrar la pista de baile y hacer que la noche fuera una inolvidable!
